(355, '_transient_dash_de3249c4736ad3bd2cd29147c4a0d43e', '<h4>Mais populares</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/plugins/jetpack/''>Jetpack by WordPress.com</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=jetpack&amp;_wpnonce=a7e3109d0a&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Jetpack by WordPress.com''>Instalar</a>)</span>\n<p>Supercharge your WordPress site with powerful features previously only available to WordPress.com users.</p>\n<h4>Plugins mais recentes</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-pie-maintenance-mode/''>Easy Pie Maintenance Mode</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=easy-pie-maintenance-mode&amp;_wpnonce=0097f08df5&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Easy Pie Maintenance Mode''>Instalar</a>)</span>\n<p>Let website visitors know your site is temporarily down while you&#039;re working on it.</p>\n', 'no'),
